<p><strong>1</strong></p>
<p>one</p>
<p><strong>浮来青旅游度假区</strong></p>
<p><strong>赏茶、采茶、品茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/737581915bb9468ab377908c961b437c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">浮来青旅游度假区是一处集旅游观光、休闲度假、餐饮住宿、培训学习一体的AAAA级景区。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/b866a695eba946baa0adc50c303947c0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
